{"tid":2373758,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！QQ 被發現登入 10 分鐘後　自動掃描瀏覽器 History","createTime":"2021-01-20T16:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T04:33:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8dcee7176633de9ec1c919b992cf36268becc4","tid":2373758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"不少跟中國工作上有來往的人也需要用 QQ，不過有沒有想過 QQ 會悄悄將你 Chrome 的 History 掃描？一位中國網友 mengyx 近日在創意工作者論壇 V2EX 上貼文，指出 QQ 會在登入後 10 分鐘自動掃描用戶電腦裡的 Appdata\\Local\\ 文件夾，而對User Data\\Default\\History  更作進一步的掃描。而 User Data\\Default\\History  是 Chrome 的預設 History 路徑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，另一位網民 qwqdanchun 進行了一些調查並進行了反編譯追蹤，他發現 QQ 確實會掃描 User Data\\Default\\History 但不一定是針對 Chrome ，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>而是所有用 Chromium 內核的瀏覽器，包括 Microsoft Edge 及大量中國瀏覽器</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQQ 掃描後，更將讀到的資料寫進 Temp 資料夾內的一個名為 temphis.db 的檔案，而經解讀後發現內裡全是電腦瀏覽過的網站資料。此外，QQ 的企業版 (TIM) 同樣會像 QQ 一般掃描用戶的瀏覽器 History。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/20/qq-access-chrome-history/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2Fqq-access-chrome-history%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia3jL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=7885f03f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2021/01/20/qq-access-chrome-history/</a>"},{"pid":"75fbced2b7ef4ff065d4ed40eb729862c3fe3488","tid":2373758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T16:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8d2a4a55f38a3b20c88425de357aed870d7763","tid":2373758,"uid":70487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20